---
/**
 * Icon Component
 * 
 * Renders inline SVG icons using Lucide icons at build time (zero client JS).
 * Icons are tree-shaken — only icons used in the site are included in the build.
 *
 * Lucide provides 1500+ consistent, beautifully crafted open source icons.
 * https://lucide.dev/icons/
 */

